QuestData.Title: Broken Traditions, Broken Bodies
QuestData.Description:
My fellow furbolg are no longer themselves. They have done... bad things. Now, they have become worse things.
Furbolg has never fought furbolg!
My brother and I escaped them. I came here looking for help. He remains by our clan's den.
Help us before our clan is lost!
QuestData.LogDescription: Meet Garz and Narn on the way to Rustpine Den.
QuestData.RewardText:
My brother spoke the truth.
It is even worse than when I left.
